* [`d_3`] = [`[$d3]`] [`\textrm{m}`]

* [`\theta`] = [`[$deg]`] [`^{\circ}`]

Determine the magnitude of the horizontal and vertical force exerted on pin [`C`] if [`F`] = [`[$f]`] [`\textrm{N}`]

[`C_x`] = [____]{$Cx} [`\textrm{N}`]

[`C_y`] = [____]{$Cy} [`\textrm{N}`]


